## Summarizing a response

Look for fields of type `text`, `short_text`, or `long_text`. Concatenate their values into a string.

Use the openai API to summarize the string into 3 key points. 

Here’s an example of using openai to summarize text:

```python
import os
import openai
openai.api_key = os.getenv("OPENAI_API_KEY")

completion = openai.ChatCompletion.create(
  model="gpt-3.5-turbo",
  messages=[
    {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Summarize the following text into 3 key points"},
    {"role": "user", "content": textFromTypeform}
  ]
)
```

